        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You're incredibly skilled in iruxi astrology, and you can gain useful (if cryptic) hints from the stars' alignment. Once per night, if you can clearly see the stars, you can spend 1 hour reading the heavens to see how they relate to a particular goal, event, or activity that will occur within 1 week. The GM rolls a secret check, either a <a class=\"inline-check with-repost\" data-pf2-traits=\"secret,lizardfolk\" data-pf2-repost-flavor=\"Read The Stars\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\" data-pf2-label=\"Read The Stars DC\" data-pf2-check=\"astrology-lore\" data-roller-role=\"origin\" data-item-uuid=\"Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.DhqsKns2SaGcOKO9\" data-pf2-dc=\"28\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-dice-d20 icon\"></i><span class=\"label\"><span data-visibility=\"gm\">DC 28</span> Astrology Lore</span><i class=\"fa-solid fa-comment-alt\" data-pf2-repost=\"\" title=\"Post prompt to chat\"></i></a> check or a <a class=\"inline-check with-repost\" data-pf2-traits=\"secret,lizardfolk\" data-pf2-repost-flavor=\"Read The Stars\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\" data-pf2-label=\"Read The Stars DC\" data-pf2-check=\"occultism\" data-roller-role=\"origin\" data-item-uuid=\"Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.DhqsKns2SaGcOKO9\" data-pf2-dc=\"32\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-dice-d20 icon\"></i><span class=\"label\"><span data-visibility=\"gm\">DC 32</span> Occultism</span><i class=\"fa-solid fa-comment-alt\" data-pf2-repost=\"\" title=\"Post prompt to chat\"></i></a> check. On a success, you learn a cryptic clue or piece of advice that could help with the chosen event, and on a critical failure, you learn a misleading cryptic clue or piece of advice.</p>"
        },
